## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of recent data and the evolving nature of cannabis research. Some sources may have inherent biases, particularly those with vested interests in the cannabis industry. Additionally, the long-term effects of cannabis legalization on public health and safety remain uncertain, necessitating ongoing research and monitoring.

